title: Twitch Bans Gambling Ft. Yung Gravy - Off The Rails #49
description: Today we wade into the absolute mess going on with Twitch right now. We are then joined by Yung Gravy! We chat about the Addison Rae/Monty situation, Ethan shows him some of his favorite videos, they share a passionate moment, dig into the Adam Levine situation, and much more!
